item.title: IntelliJ Plugin: Java Development
item.description: This post presents some of the plugins of IntelliJ that can be useful during daily work. These plugins are used mostly to develop Java related projects, and give a huge support in effective programming. Some of them are language or project agnostic. Recommendation is represented as a list of star. Five is the most, zero is the lowest. Material Theme UI ⭐ ⭐ ⭐ ⭐ ⭐ Rich, awesome, and configurable UI design to bring the best out of the look of your IDE.
